These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling, baseball, tennis
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, snooker, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, july, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, spy, time-travel, romance
 1. the person watching spy movies is the person playing domino##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 7. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 8. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
11. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Sport          | tennis     | cycling   | snowboarding | baseball |
| Game   | domino | scrabble    | monopoly   | snooker    |
| Birthday           | july       | june   | august   | march     |
| Movie-Genre     | spy       | action | romance  | time-travel      |

