.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster, baccarat, alhambra
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer, videographer, chef
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading, fishing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, classical, metal
 1. the videographer is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the chef is somewhere to the right of the fan of metal##5
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the software-developer is between the chef and the bluemaster-smoker##2
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is the chef##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
11. the fan of house is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar      | bluemaster       | siglo | alhambra     | baccarat     |
| Job   | freelancer      | software-developer       | chef | videographer |
| Hobby           | fishing       | rock-climbing    | reading     | magic-tricks         |
| Music-Genre     | metal | classical     | house     | salsa       |

