.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco, tower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, weightlifting, tennis
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, mirinda, iced-tea
City: prague, edinburgh, rome, new-york
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 9. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person traveling to prague##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| House          | tower    | art-deco      | gothic-revival   | farmhouse |
| Sport   | climbing | weightlifting | skateboarding | tennis  |
| Beverage   | tea   | mirinda         | soy-milk  | iced-tea  |
| City           | rome      | prague          | new-york | edinburgh  |

