 5. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person traveling to rome and the person driving the ship##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
11. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
13. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5

