 1. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
 2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the brazilian##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 5. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
 6. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 7. the british is on the left of the cottage house##1
 8. the russian is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 9. the cottage house is the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
11. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the brazilian is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
