 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 9. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
10. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
11. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
12. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
13. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5

