 9. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the musician is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
12. the mechanic is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
13. the fan of classical is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
