10. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is the townhouse house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |         3          |     4      |
| House          | palace         | townhouse         | victorian             | gothic-revival     |
| Color           | coral | purple | red | yellow   |
| Cigar   | siglo   | ritmeester    | swisher            | dunhill        |
| Birthday         | november      | june      | october           | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, disco, hip-hop, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, ivory, white
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, car, trike
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, photography, cooking, camping
 1. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
 2. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person driving the tram is between the fan of pop and the person driving the trike##2
 4. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
 6. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 8. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 9. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
12. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Music-Genre      | r&b   | pop | disco   | hip-hop          |
| Color          | emerald    | white        | ivory     | lavender          |
| Transport           | snowmobile | car        | tram | trike |
| Hobby   | camping    | singing     | cooking      | photography        |

