.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, july, march
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, dancing, filmmaking, chess
There 4 different types of food: spinach, lemon, radish, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, indonesian, japanese
 1. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 4. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person eating pomegranate##2
 6. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
10. the mexican is on the right of the japanese##1
11. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
13. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday      | july   | march      | june | october     |
| Hobby           | chess   | collecting  | dancing        | filmmaking |
| Food   | spinach     | pomegranate     | radish      | lemon   |
| Nationality     | brazilian | indonesian | japanese          | mexican     |

