.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, thai, chinese, canadian
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, blood-red, brown
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, billiard, snooker
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, rat, guinea-pig
 1. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the malaysian##1
 3. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 4. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
 7. the person who likes blood-red is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the malaysian##1
10. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
11. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
12. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality          | malaysian | chinese  | canadian    | thai       |
| Color           | azure  | brown | blood-red | chestnut  |
| Game   | scrabble    | billiard   | snooker  | chess     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig      | rat    | horse        | hedgehog |

 